11:21.899 --> 11:23.019
Woher kennst du Ruan Yu

11:23.139 --> 11:24.220
Ich bin Ruan Yus beste

11:25.379 --> 11:25.859
Freundin

11:29.979 --> 11:30.499
beste Freundin

11:31.139 --> 11:31.859
beste Freundin

